# main part, [[majority]]
# [[most]] of
#: {{ux|fr|Il a mangé '''la plupart''' du gâteau|translation=He ate most of the cake.}}
#: {{ux|fr|'''La plupart''' des gens aiment le chocolat|translation=Most people like chocolate.}}
#: {{ux|fr|'''La plupart''' d'entre eux se sont quand même partis|translation=Most of them have left, anyway.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Il existe une cinquantaine de radioéléments naturels dont '''la plupart''' font partie des trois familles naturelles du thorium, de l'uranium et de l'actinium|translation=There are around 50 natural radioelements, most of which belong to the natural families of thorium, uranium, and actinium.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Les châteaux valdôtains, auxquels est indissociablement liée l'histoire de la Vallée d'Aoste, autrefois principal moyen de défense, sont aujourd'hui une des plus importantes richesses de la plus petite région italienne. En dépit de ses dimensions, en la parcourant on peut trouver presque un château dans chaque village, dont '''la plupart''' ont été bien conservés, et constituent une des majeures attractions touristiques|translation=The castles of the Aosta Valley, to which the history of the Aosta Valley is inextricably linked, once its principal means of defense, are today one of the most important assets of the smallest region of Italy. Despite its size, in almost every village there is a castle, most of which have been well-preserved, and are a major tourist attraction.}}

====Usage notes====
While its near synonym {{m|fr|majorité}} can accord with both singular and plural forms of verbs, adjectives, etc., when {{m|fr|la [[plupart]]}} is linked to a verb, participle, adjective or pronoun, the form of the latter follows the grammatical gender and number of the noun to which the former is connected by the preposition {{l|fr|de}}. When used without clear connection to some nominal unit, the masculine plural is used.
* {{uxi|fr|La plupart de ce travail est trop compliqué.|Most of this work is too complicated.}} {{q|masculine singular agreement with {{m|fr|travail}}}}
* {{uxi|fr|La plupart de mes amis sont américains.|Most of my friends are American.}} {{q|masculine plural agreement with {{m|fr|amis}}}}
* {{uxi|fr|La plupart de la population est folle.|Most of the population is mad.}} {{q|feminine singular agreement with {{m|fr|population}}}}
* {{uxi|fr|La plupart des étoiles sont plus grandes que le Soleil.|Most stars are bigger than the Sun.}} {{q|feminine plural agreement with {{m|fr|étoiles}}}}

